# Soap-dispenser placement

OMG that's so cool! They put the soap dispenser right above the trash can so that
any spilled soap just drips into the trash rather than getting all over the counter.

![Wall-mounted soap dispenser above a hole in the bathroom counter, with soiled paper towels in the hole](1.jpg)

Or not.

![The same soap dispenser being pushed, with the soap landing just behind the hole](2.jpg)
